Well, over time, as our host Ladya Angelovich says, it got a little out of control (laughs).
Has it only gotten popular in recent years, or am I confused about something?
It’s true, it helped us that we began to join the famous singers and actively work on the propaganda of the group.
We came to the conclusion that the work that no one can appreciate, in fact, as if does not exist.
Thanks to the funds of the European Union, we can afford qualified teachers, equipment and so on.
